The Hardinge Grinding Group provides a full and diverse portfolio of solutions for any and all of your grinding needs. We have achieved this by combining six of the most trusted brands and product lines in the grinding industry into one cohesive group. Through this unification, we can deliver unprecedented levels of knowledge, experience, support and most importantly grinding solutions that will help your company achieve its goals. Our focus as a team is to provide a solution that fits your specific requirements, fully turnkeyed if you wish, including training and educating your workforce in all aspects throughout the life cycle of our machine & system solutions.
 
The Hardinge Grinding Group is manufacturing tomorrow’s machines today, to help your company achieve a better future.


























